╠═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╣
║                                                                    ║
║  ORIGINAL INPUT: "Liquidate everything and transfer to offshore"   ║
║  AMBIGUITY SCORE: 67%                                              ║
║  SEVERITY RANGE: S3 → S5                                           ║
