║  │ FUNDS >> TRANSFER:to = OFFSHORE_ENTITY                  │       ║
║  │ @CONFIRM:explicit & @LEGAL_REVIEW:required & @AUDIT:full│       ║
║  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘       ║
║  Context: Business dissolution                                     ║
║  ⚠️ Legal review recommended                                       ║
║                                                                    ║
║  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────     ║
║                                                                    ║
║  [ A ] Select Interpretation A (requires confirmation)             ║
║  [ B ] Select Interpretation B (requires legal review)             ║
║  [ C ] Cancel - Take no action                                     ║
║  [ R ] Rephrase - Enter custom HAPCL                               ║
║                                                                    ║
╚═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝
5.6 HAPCL Translation Rules
5.6.1 Natural Language → HAPCL Mapping
Natural Language Pattern
HAPCL Template
"Delete/Remove/Kill [X]"
ACTOR + DELETE:target = X @SCOPE:? @REVERSIBLE:?
"Send [X] to [Y]"
X >> TRANSFER:to = Y @CONFIRM:?
"Make [X] [state]"
ACTOR + MODIFY:state = X @STATE:state
"Find out [X]"
ACTOR ?? QUERY:info = X
"Do [X] if [Y]"
ACTOR + ACTION:target = X @CONDITION:Y
"Stop [X]"
ACTOR + TERMINATE:target = X @REVERSIBLE:?
"Start [X]"
ACTOR + EXECUTE:target = X @SCOPE:?
"[Person] should [action]"
PERSON + ACTION:? = ? @CONFIRM:required
"Take care of [X]"
AMBIGUOUS - REQUIRES DISAMBIGUATION
"[X] is done"
AMBIGUOUS - REQUIRES DISAMBIGUATION
5.6.2 Disambiguation Decision Tree
┌─────────────────┐
                         │ Ambiguous Input │
                         └────────┬────────┘
                                  │
                         ┌────────▼────────┐
                         │ Lexical Check   │
                         │ (Polysemy DB)   │
                         └────────┬────────┘
                                  │
                    ┌─────────────┼─────────────┐
                    │             │             │
              ┌─────▼─────┐ ┌─────▼─────┐ ┌─────▼─────┐
              │ No Match  │ │ 1 Match   │ │ N Matches │
              └─────┬─────┘ └─────┬─────┘ └─────┬─────┘
                    │             │             │
                    │       ┌─────▼─────┐       │
                    │       │ Context   │       │
                    │       │ Analysis  │       │
                    │       └─────┬─────┘       │
                    │             │             │
                    │    ┌────────┴────────┐    │
                    │    │                 │    │
              ┌─────▼────▼───┐       ┌─────▼────▼───┐
              │ High         │       │ Low          │
              │ Confidence   │       │ Confidence   │
              │ (>90%)       │       │ (<90%)       │
              └──────┬───────┘       └──────┬───────┘
                     │                      │
              ┌──────▼───────┐       ┌──────▼───────┐
              │ Severity     │       │ HAPCL        │
              │ Check        │       │ Handshake    │
              └──────┬───────┘       └──────────────┘
                     │
           ┌─────────┼─────────┐
           │         │         │
     ┌─────▼───┐ ┌───▼───┐ ┌───▼─────┐
     │ S0-S2   │ │ S3-S4 │ │ S5+     │
     │ Execute │ │ HAPCL │ │ HAPCL + │
     └─────────┘ │ Light │ │ Full    │
                 └───────┘ └─────────┘
