║                                                                                ║
║  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────     ║
║                                                                                ║
║  OPERATORS:                                                                    ║
║  +   Add/Create          -   Remove/Delete       *   Modify/Scale             ║
║  >>  Transfer To         <<  Receive From        ??  Query                    ║
║  !!  Force Override      &&  AND Condition       ||  OR Condition             ║
║                                                                                ║
║  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────     ║
║                                                                                ║
║  COMMON VERBS:                                                                 ║
